DISCIPLINARY CASES

2008-1604. In re Resignation of Gottlieb.

This matter came on for consideration on August 12, 2008, upon the filing by the Office of Attorney Services of an application for retirement or resignation and the sealed report of Disciplinary Counsel. Upon consideration thereof,

It is ordered by the court, sua sponte, that the application and report are stricken, and this cause is hereby dismissed.
